title: G-SHOCK X GREATS : Event Recap
description:
On April 14th, guests were invited to G-Shock’s Soho location to celebrate the launch of Fade to White, a collaboration between G-Shock, and Brooklyn based footwear label Greats.

Among notable attendees were, Ryan Babenzien, founder of Greats as well as influencers from across fashion and streetwear.

The event hosted over 210 guests with music by DJ Pamela Katz.
